he criticism, she said, has been fueled by hate.\", \"from\": 5098, \"to\": 5147, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The criticism\", \"from\": 5098, \"to\": 5111}, {\"ngram\": \"hate\", \"from\": 5142, \"to\": 5146}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Where is the Catholicism, the Christianity in that?\", \"from\": 5148, \"to\": 5200, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5179, \"end\": 5191, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.9999999609344749, \"rank\": 3.90501313526276e-08, \"text\": \"Christianity\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Catholicism\", \"from\": 5158, \"to\": 5173}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It is very hypocritical that their message is not about religion or kindness, it's about hate towards Jews, fat people, queer people and trans people.\\\"\", \"from\": 5201, \"to\": 5352, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5303, \"end\": 5307, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jews\", \"score\": 0.9953264652611407, \"rank\": 0.0046954717598139285, \"text\": \"Jews\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jews\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jews\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"their message\", \"from\": 5230, \"to\": 5243}, {\"ngram\": \"religion\", \"from\": 5257, \"to\": 5265}, {\"ngram\": \"kindness\", \"from\": 5269, \"to\": 5277}, {\"ngram\": \"hate\", \"from\": 5290, \"to\": 5294}, {\"ngram\": \"fat people\", \"from\": 5309, \"to\": 5319}, {\"ngram\": \"queer people\", \"from\": 5321, \"to\": 5333}, {\"ngram\": \"trans\", \"from\": 5338, \"to\": 5343}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 5344, \"to\": 5350}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We have been accused of trying to impose our vision on the world,\\\" Bardin said.\", \"from\": 5354, \"to\": 5434, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"our vision\", \"from\": 5396, \"to\": 5406}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 5410, \"to\": 5419}, {\"ngram\": \"Bardin\", \"from\": 5422, \"to\": 5428}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We are not.\", \"from\": 5435, \"to\": 5447, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u2026 We just want to let people know that we have a place in the world, and we are claiming that place.\\\"\", \"from\": 5448, \"to\": 5549, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 5470, \"to\": 5476}, {\"ngram\": \"a place\", \"from\": 5495, \"to\": 5502}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 5506, \"to\": 5515}, {\"ngram\": \"that place\", \"from\": 5537, \"to\": 5547}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Paloma spoke to the AP in a phone interview and later at her Paris workshop, a studio devoted to her drag performance.\", \"from\": 5551, \"to\": 5669, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5551, \"end\": 5557, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paloma_Picasso\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.317560137786877e-16, \"text\": \"Paloma\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paloma_Picasso\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paloma_Picasso\"}, {\"begin\": 5571, \"end\": 5573, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.118369511608019e-16, \"text\": \"AP\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\"}, {\"begin\": 5612, \"end\": 5617, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.3941025779054645e-15, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a phone interview\", \"from\": 5577, \"to\": 5594}, {\"ngram\": \"a studio\", \"from\": 5628, \"to\": 5636}, {\"ngram\": \"her drag performance\", \"from\": 5648, \"to\": 5668}]}, {\"sente